# FabEdge FDC console — no backend required. The console runs entirely
# client-side; these are optional.

# AI stand-in tier (/api/explain, /api/chat) — hosted analog of the kit's
# on-prem SUSE AI tier (Ollama). Without it the routes degrade gracefully and
# the console falls back to the deterministic signature diagnosis.
# Set the same variable on the Vercel project (Production + Preview).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# Optional model override (default claude-opus-4-8)
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=
